ZH: 我的屋子很小。
EN: My house is very small.

ZH: 在这个屋子里有很多书籍。
EN: There are many books in this room.

ZH: 我们在这个屋里看电影。
EN: We watch movies in this house.

ZH: 这个屋子的屋顶正在修理中。
EN: The roof of this house is being repaired.

ZH: 这栋屋子有三个卧室。
EN: This house has three bedrooms.

ZH: 我的朋友住在三层楼的屋子里。
EN: My friend lives in a three-story house.

ZH: 在老屋子里有悠久的历史。
EN: The old house has a long history.

ZH: 我喜欢在屋里种花。
EN: I like to grow flowers in the house.

ZH: 今晚我会打扫我的屋子。
EN: I will clean my house tonight.

ZH: 在这座山上有一座漂亮的木屋。
EN: There is a beautiful wooden house on this mountain.

ZH: 这所房子是一个古老的屋。
EN: This house is an ancient building.

ZH: 屋子里的家具非常漂亮。
EN: The furniture in the house is very beautiful.

ZH: 这是一座被废弃的古老屋。
EN: This is an abandoned old house.

ZH: 我喜欢在我的屋里放一些艺术品。
EN: I like to put some art pieces in my house.

ZH: 他是一位建筑师，设计了这座美丽的屋。
EN: He is an architect who designed this beautiful house.

ZH: 我每天早上在我的小屋里喝咖啡。
EN: I drink coffee in my small cabin every morning.

ZH: 这个小孩在屋里玩耍。
EN: The kid is playing in the house.

ZH: 这座屋子有很多窗户。
EN: This house has many windows.

ZH: 他在小屋里创作了许多音乐作品。
EN: He created many music pieces in the cabin.

ZH: 在我的屋子里有一台钢琴。
EN: There is a piano in my house.
